      <url href="https://github.com/rstudio/bookdown"
      visual="github.com/rstudio/bookdown"/>.
    </p>

    <p>
      This PreTeXt edition was prepared by
      <url href="https://github.com/PreTeXtBooks/bookdown"
      visual="github.com/PreTeXtBooks/bookdown">the PreTeXtBooks project</url>
      to make the content available in the PreTeXt format, enabling accessible
      and structured output in HTML, PDF, and other formats. All prose, code
      examples, figures, and mathematical content are intended to be faithful
      reproductions of the original work, though occasional typographical errors
      may have been introduced in the conversion process. Report any issues to
      our
      <url href="https://github.com/PreTeXtBooks/bookdown/issues"
      visual="github.com/PreTeXtBooks/bookdown/issues">GitHub Issues Page</url>.
    </p>

